7 July 2008Government will hold cluster media briefings on the implementation of the Government Programme of Action for 2008 in Pretoria from 30 June to 8 July 2008.This will be the second cycle of media briefings for the year since the announcement of the programme through the State of the Nation Address.The briefings will take place at the Union Buildings, Rooms 153 and 159. There will be a video link-up with Cape Town's Imbizo Media Centre, 120 Plein Street, Cape Town.Social Cluster briefing schedule:Tuesday, 8 July 200812:00 13:30 Social Cluster, chaired by Minister of Health Manto Tshabalala-Msimang Venue: Room 153, Union Buildings, PretoriaEnquiries Harold Maloka (Pretoria) Cell: 082 847 9799Colin Cruywagen (Cape Town) Cell: 082 377 9916Issued by: Government Communications (GCIS)